{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":397,"text":"When we talk about corruption,"},{"time":2852,"text":"there are typical types\nof individuals that spring to mind."},{"time":6322,"text":"There's the former Soviet megalomaniacs."},{"time":8650,"text":"Saparmurat Niyazov, he was one of them."},{"time":11839,"text":"Until his death in 2006,"},{"time":13827,"text":"he was the all-powerful\nleader of Turkmenistan,"},{"time":17133,"text":"a Central Asian country\nrich in natural gas."},{"time":20898,"text":"Now, he really loved to issue\npresidential decrees."},{"time":24848,"text":"And one renamed the months of the year"},{"time":27093,"text":"including after himself and his mother."},{"time":30243,"text":"He spent millions of dollars"},{"time":32277,"text":"creating a bizarre personality cult,"},{"time":35097,"text":"and his crowning glory was the building"},{"time":37066,"text":"of a 40-foot-high gold-plated\nstatue of himself"},{"time":41106,"text":"which stood proudly\nin the capital's central square"},{"time":44170,"text":"and rotated to follow the sun."},{"time":47162,"text":"He was a slightly unusual guy."},{"time":49935,"text":"And then there's that cliché,"},{"time":51792,"text":"the African dictator\nor minister or official."},{"time":55191,"text":"There's Teodorín Obiang."},{"time":58302,"text":"So his daddy is president\nfor life of Equatorial Guinea,"},{"time":62533,"text":"a West African nation that has exported"},{"time":65657,"text":"billions of dollars of oil since the 1990s"},{"time":69138,"text":"and yet has a truly appalling\nhuman rights record."},{"time":73182,"text":"The vast majority of its people"},{"time":75076,"text":"are living in really miserable poverty"},{"time":78031,"text":"despite an income\nper capita that's on a par"},{"time":80151,"text":"with that of Portugal."},{"time":82649,"text":"So Obiang junior, well, he buys himself"},{"time":85354,"text":"a $30 million mansion\nin Malibu, California."},{"time":89786,"text":"I've been up to its front gates."},{"time":90887,"text":"I can tell you it's a magnificent spread."},{"time":93982,"text":"He bought an €18 million art collection"},{"time":97701,"text":"that used to belong to fashion\ndesigner Yves Saint Laurent,"},{"time":101840,"text":"a stack of fabulous sports cars,"},{"time":103388,"text":"some costing a million dollars apiece --"},{"time":105943,"text":"oh, and a Gulfstream jet, too."},{"time":108259,"text":"Now get this:"},{"time":109620,"text":"Until recently, he was earning\nan official monthly salary"},{"time":113761,"text":"of less than 7,000 dollars."},{"time":117915,"text":"And there's Dan Etete."},{"time":119968,"text":"Well, he was the former\noil minister of Nigeria"},{"time":122612,"text":"under President Abacha,"},{"time":124586,"text":"and it just so happens\nhe's a convicted money launderer too."},{"time":128088,"text":"We've spent a great deal of time"},{"time":130330,"text":"investigating a $1 billion --"},{"time":132731,"text":"that's right, a $1 billion —"},{"time":134494,"text":"oil deal that he was involved with,"},{"time":137155,"text":"and what we found was pretty shocking,"},{"time":139107,"text":"but more about that later."},{"time":141873,"text":"So it's easy to think\nthat corruption happens"},{"time":145390,"text":"somewhere over there,"},{"time":147250,"text":"carried out by a bunch of greedy despots"},{"time":149706,"text":"and individuals up to no good in countries"},{"time":151730,"text":"that we, personally, may\nknow very little about"},{"time":154738,"text":"and feel really unconnected to"},{"time":156427,"text":"and unaffected by what might be going on."},{"time":159915,"text":"But does it just happen over there?"},{"time":163158,"text":"Well, at 22, I was very lucky."},{"time":166437,"text":"My first job out of university"},{"time":169218,"text":"was investigating the illegal\ntrade in African ivory."},{"time":173202,"text":"And that's how my relationship\nwith corruption really began."},{"time":177431,"text":"In 1993, with two friends\nwho were colleagues,"},{"time":180439,"text":"Simon Taylor and Patrick Alley,"},{"time":183242,"text":"we set up an organization\ncalled Global Witness."},{"time":186843,"text":"Our first campaign\nwas investigating the role"},{"time":189593,"text":"of illegal logging in funding\nthe war in Cambodia."},{"time":193899,"text":"So a few years later, and it's now 1997,"},{"time":196942,"text":"and I'm in Angola undercover\ninvestigating blood diamonds."},{"time":201703,"text":"Perhaps you saw the film,"},{"time":203430,"text":"the Hollywood film \"Blood Diamond,\""},{"time":205121,"text":"the one with Leonardo DiCaprio."},{"time":206698,"text":"Well, some of that sprang from our work."},{"time":210153,"text":"Luanda, it was full of land mine victims"},{"time":212869,"text":"who were struggling\nto survive on the streets"},{"time":215049,"text":"and war orphans living\nin sewers under the streets,"},{"time":218137,"text":"and a tiny, very wealthy elite"},{"time":220226,"text":"who gossiped about shopping\ntrips to Brazil and Portugal."},{"time":223445,"text":"And it was a slightly crazy place."},{"time":226206,"text":"So I'm sitting in a hot\nand very stuffy hotel room"},{"time":229890,"text":"feeling just totally overwhelmed."},{"time":232950,"text":"But it wasn't about blood diamonds."},{"time":235306,"text":"Because I'd been speaking\nto lots of people there"},{"time":238208,"text":"who, well, they talked\nabout a different problem:"},{"time":240576,"text":"that of a massive web\nof corruption on a global scale"},{"time":243997,"text":"and millions of oil dollars going missing."},{"time":247331,"text":"And for what was then\na very small organization"},{"time":249792,"text":"of just a few people,"},{"time":251940,"text":"trying to even begin to think\nhow we might tackle that"},{"time":254682,"text":"was an enormous challenge."},{"time":257153,"text":"And in the years that I've been,"},{"time":258701,"text":"and we've all been campaigning\nand investigating,"},{"time":261255,"text":"I've repeatedly seen\nthat what makes corruption"},{"time":263519,"text":"on a global, massive scale possible,"},{"time":265787,"text":"well it isn't just greed\nor the misuse of power"},{"time":268921,"text":"or that nebulous phrase \"weak governance.\""},{"time":271360,"text":"I mean, yes, it's all of those,"},{"time":273397,"text":"but corruption, it's made\npossible by the actions"},{"time":276349,"text":"of global facilitators."},{"time":279970,"text":"So let's go back to some of those\npeople I talked about earlier."},{"time":283160,"text":"Now, they're all people\nwe've investigated,"},{"time":284677,"text":"and they're all people who couldn't\ndo what they do alone."},{"time":287463,"text":"Take Obiang junior. Well, he didn't end up"},{"time":289903,"text":"with high-end art and luxury\nhouses without help."},{"time":293742,"text":"He did business with global banks."},{"time":295917,"text":"A bank in Paris held accounts\nof companies controlled by him,"},{"time":299756,"text":"one of which was used to buy the art,"},{"time":302154,"text":"and American banks, well, they funneled"},{"time":304795,"text":"73 million dollars into the States,"},{"time":307731,"text":"some of which was used to buy\nthat California mansion."},{"time":311830,"text":"And he didn't do all of this\nin his own name either."},{"time":314738,"text":"He used shell companies."},{"time":316492,"text":"He used one to buy\nthe property, and another,"},{"time":318826,"text":"which was in somebody else's name,"},{"time":320912,"text":"to pay the huge bills it\ncost to run the place."},{"time":324910,"text":"And then there's Dan Etete."},{"time":327138,"text":"Well, when he was oil minister,"},{"time":329220,"text":"he awarded an oil block now\nworth over a billion dollars"},{"time":334350,"text":"to a company that, guess what, yeah,"},{"time":337184,"text":"he was the hidden owner of."},{"time":339567,"text":"Now, it was then much later traded on"},{"time":342969,"text":"with the kind assistance\nof the Nigerian government --"},{"time":345565,"text":"now I have to be careful what I say here —"},{"time":347647,"text":"to subsidiaries of Shell\nand the Italian Eni,"},{"time":351796,"text":"two of the biggest oil companies around."},{"time":354450,"text":"So the reality is,\nis that the engine of corruption,"},{"time":356903,"text":"well, it exists far\nbeyond the shores of countries"},{"time":359346,"text":"like Equatorial Guinea\nor Nigeria or Turkmenistan."},{"time":362545,"text":"This engine, well, it's driven"},{"time":364869,"text":"by our international banking system,"},{"time":367235,"text":"by the problem of anonymous\nshell companies,"},{"time":369778,"text":"and by the secrecy that we have afforded"},{"time":372160,"text":"big oil, gas and mining operations,"},{"time":375129,"text":"and, most of all, by the failure\nof our politicians"},{"time":378862,"text":"to back up their rhetoric and do something"},{"time":380937,"text":"really meaningful and systemic\nto tackle this stuff."},{"time":385929,"text":"Now let's take the banks first."},{"time":387940,"text":"Well, it's not going\nto come as any surprise"},{"time":390274,"text":"for me to tell you that banks\naccept dirty money,"},{"time":394586,"text":"but they prioritize their profits\nin other destructive ways too."},{"time":399130,"text":"For example, in Sarawak, Malaysia."},{"time":402237,"text":"Now this region, it has just five percent"},{"time":405876,"text":"of its forests left intact. Five percent."},{"time":411292,"text":"So how did that happen?"},{"time":412627,"text":"Well, because an elite\nand its facilitators"},{"time":415683,"text":"have been making millions of dollars"},{"time":417857,"text":"from supporting logging\non an industrial scale"},{"time":421388,"text":"for many years."},{"time":423794,"text":"So we sent an undercover investigator in"},{"time":426048,"text":"to secretly film meetings\nwith members of the ruling elite,"},{"time":429638,"text":"and the resulting footage, well,\nit made some people very angry,"},{"time":432969,"text":"and you can see that on YouTube,"},{"time":435219,"text":"but it proved what we had long suspected,"},{"time":437196,"text":"because it showed\nhow the state's chief minister,"},{"time":440693,"text":"despite his later denials,"},{"time":442603,"text":"used his control over land\nand forest licenses"},{"time":446002,"text":"to enrich himself and his family."},{"time":449033,"text":"And HSBC, well, we know\nthat HSBC bankrolled"},{"time":453632,"text":"the region's largest logging companies"},{"time":455641,"text":"that were responsible\nfor some of that destruction"},{"time":458046,"text":"in Sarawak and elsewhere."},{"time":460633,"text":"The bank violated its own\nsustainability policies in the process,"},{"time":464341,"text":"but it earned around 130 million dollars."},{"time":468161,"text":"Now shortly after our exposé,"},{"time":470497,"text":"very shortly after our exposé\nearlier this year,"},{"time":473099,"text":"the bank announced\na policy review on this."},{"time":476103,"text":"And is this progress? Maybe,"},{"time":478689,"text":"but we're going to be\nkeeping a very close eye"},{"time":481192,"text":"on that case."},{"time":483529,"text":"And then there's the problem\nof anonymous shell companies."},{"time":486942,"text":"Well, we've all heard\nabout what they are, I think,"},{"time":489771,"text":"and we all know they're used quite a bit"},{"time":492267,"text":"by people and companies\nwho are trying to avoid"},{"time":494853,"text":"paying their proper dues to society,"},{"time":497900,"text":"also known as taxes."},{"time":499953,"text":"But what doesn't usually come to light"},{"time":502862,"text":"is how shell companies are used to steal"},{"time":507412,"text":"huge sums of money,\ntransformational sums of money,"},{"time":510784,"text":"from poor countries."},{"time":512830,"text":"In virtually every case of corruption\nthat we've investigated,"},{"time":516250,"text":"shell companies have appeared,"},{"time":518462,"text":"and sometimes\nit's been impossible to find out"},{"time":520822,"text":"who is really involved in the deal."},{"time":524334,"text":"A recent study by the World Bank"},{"time":526662,"text":"looked at 200 cases of corruption."},{"time":529612,"text":"It found that over 70\npercent of those cases"},{"time":532702,"text":"had used anonymous shell companies,"},{"time":535656,"text":"totaling almost 56 billion dollars."},{"time":539038,"text":"Now many of these\ncompanies were in America"},{"time":541300,"text":"or the United Kingdom,"},{"time":542610,"text":"its overseas territories\nand Crown dependencies,"},{"time":545011,"text":"and so it's not just an offshore problem,"},{"time":547265,"text":"it's an on-shore one too."},{"time":549557,"text":"You see, shell companies, they're central"},{"time":551696,"text":"to the secret deals which may\nbenefit wealthy elites"},{"time":554950,"text":"rather than ordinary citizens."},{"time":557974,"text":"One striking recent case\nthat we've investigated"},{"time":561220,"text":"is how the government\nin the Democratic Republic of Congo"},{"time":564196,"text":"sold off a series of valuable,\nstate-owned mining assets"},{"time":568553,"text":"to shell companies\nin the British Virgin Islands."},{"time":571907,"text":"So we spoke to sources in country,"},{"time":574179,"text":"trawled through company\ndocuments and other information"},{"time":577215,"text":"trying to piece together a really\ntrue picture of the deal."},{"time":581270,"text":"And we were alarmed to find\nthat these shell companies"},{"time":584095,"text":"had quickly flipped many of the assets on"},{"time":586611,"text":"for huge profits to major\ninternational mining companies"},{"time":590832,"text":"listed in London."},{"time":593195,"text":"Now, the Africa Progress\nPanel, led by Kofi Annan,"},{"time":596451,"text":"they've calculated\nthat Congo may have lost"},{"time":599339,"text":"more than 1.3 billion dollars\nfrom these deals."},{"time":604443,"text":"That's almost twice"},{"time":606696,"text":"the country's annual health\nand education budget combined."},{"time":612336,"text":"And will the people of Congo,\nwill they ever get their money back?"},{"time":614962,"text":"Well, the answer to that question,"},{"time":616620,"text":"and who was really involved\nand what really happened,"},{"time":618514,"text":"well that's going to probably\nremain locked away"},{"time":621017,"text":"in the secretive company registries\nof the British Virgin Islands"},{"time":624166,"text":"and elsewhere unless we all do\nsomething about it."},{"time":629000,"text":"And how about the oil, gas\nand mining companies?"},{"time":631987,"text":"Okay, maybe it's a bit\nof a cliché to talk about them."},{"time":634701,"text":"Corruption in that sector, no surprise."},{"time":636821,"text":"There's corruption everywhere,\nso why focus on that sector?"},{"time":641254,"text":"Well, because there's a lot at stake."},{"time":643454,"text":"In 2011, natural resource exports"},{"time":647551,"text":"outweighed aid flows by almost 19 to one"},{"time":651063,"text":"in Africa, Asia and Latin America.\nNineteen to one."},{"time":655486,"text":"Now that's a hell of a lot\nof schools and universities"},{"time":659123,"text":"and hospitals and business startups,"},{"time":661100,"text":"many of which haven't\nmaterialized and never will"},{"time":663458,"text":"because some of that money\nhas simply been stolen away."},{"time":667789,"text":"Now let's go back to the oil\nand mining companies,"},{"time":670194,"text":"and let's go back to Dan Etete\nand that $1 billion deal."},{"time":673210,"text":"And now forgive me, I'm\ngoing to read the next bit"},{"time":676499,"text":"because it's a very live\nissue, and our lawyers"},{"time":678796,"text":"have been through this in some detail"},{"time":680986,"text":"and they want me to get it right."},{"time":684296,"text":"Now, on the surface, the deal\nappeared straightforward."},{"time":688469,"text":"Subsidiaries of Shell and Eni"},{"time":690569,"text":"paid the Nigerian\ngovernment for the block."},{"time":693543,"text":"The Nigerian government transferred"},{"time":695706,"text":"precisely the same amount,\nto the very dollar,"},{"time":698530,"text":"to an account earmarked\nfor a shell company"},{"time":703145,"text":"whose hidden owner was Etete."},{"time":705271,"text":"Now, that's not bad going\nfor a convicted money launderer."},{"time":708660,"text":"And here's the thing."},{"time":710117,"text":"After many months of digging around"},{"time":711994,"text":"and reading through hundreds\nof pages of court documents,"},{"time":715529,"text":"we found evidence that, in fact,"},{"time":717484,"text":"Shell and Eni had known that the funds"},{"time":720913,"text":"would be transferred\nto that shell company,"},{"time":723988,"text":"and frankly, it's hard\nto believe they didn't know"},{"time":727695,"text":"who they were really dealing with there."},{"time":730986,"text":"Now, it just shouldn't take\nthese sorts of efforts"},{"time":734074,"text":"to find out where the money\nin deals like this went."},{"time":736603,"text":"I mean, these are state assets."},{"time":738172,"text":"They're supposed to be\nused for the benefit"},{"time":739638,"text":"of the people in the country."},{"time":741371,"text":"But in some countries,\ncitizens and journalists"},{"time":744560,"text":"who are trying to expose stories like this"},{"time":746584,"text":"have been harassed and arrested"},{"time":748085,"text":"and some have even risked\ntheir lives to do so."},{"time":752540,"text":"And finally, well, there\nare those who believe"},{"time":756344,"text":"that corruption is unavoidable."},{"time":758668,"text":"It's just how some business is done."},{"time":760817,"text":"It's too complex and difficult to change."},{"time":763382,"text":"So in effect, what? We just accept it."},{"time":766309,"text":"But as a campaigner and investigator,"},{"time":768702,"text":"I have a different view,"},{"time":769753,"text":"because I've seen what can happen"},{"time":771923,"text":"when an idea gains momentum."},{"time":774477,"text":"In the oil and mining sector, for example,"},{"time":777221,"text":"there is now the beginning"},{"time":778484,"text":"of a truly worldwide transparency standard"},{"time":781733,"text":"that could tackle some of these problems."},{"time":784753,"text":"In 1999, when Global Witness called"},{"time":787175,"text":"for oil companies to make\npayments on deals transparent,"},{"time":790514,"text":"well, some people laughed\nat the extreme naiveté"},{"time":794303,"text":"of that small idea."},{"time":796406,"text":"But literally hundreds\nof civil society groups"},{"time":799976,"text":"from around the world came together"},{"time":801854,"text":"to fight for transparency,"},{"time":803463,"text":"and now it's fast becoming\nthe norm and the law."},{"time":807444,"text":"Two thirds of the value"},{"time":809416,"text":"of the world's oil and mining companies"},{"time":811736,"text":"are now covered by transparency laws.\nTwo thirds."},{"time":815507,"text":"So this is change happening."},{"time":816980,"text":"This is progress."},{"time":818870,"text":"But we're not there yet, by far."},{"time":821993,"text":"Because it really isn't about corruption"},{"time":824239,"text":"somewhere over there, is it?"},{"time":826354,"text":"In a globalized world, corruption"},{"time":828559,"text":"is a truly globalized business,"},{"time":830822,"text":"and one that needs global solutions,"},{"time":832937,"text":"supported and pushed by us\nall, as global citizens,"},{"time":836937,"text":"right here."},{"time":838099,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":839289,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}